{"type": "article", "id": 20159, "title": "带彩框的柜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-04T07:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134131XJ758h0z1SNnKIbR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是西班牙设计师 Carlos Jiménez 为瑞典的家具品牌 By.Enströms 带来的柜子系列，要求使用木头并体现出传统。设计师结合了斯堪的纳维亚风格、日式的简约外形和地中海式的色彩感，方形的木柜下面有四根圆柱形的腿，柜子里都有彩色的框子，是在典雅中的一种提亮，显得活泼有趣。这组柜子可根据具体的环境调整长宽比例和抽屉的排列方式，<a href=\"http://www.carlosjimenezdesign.com/kaaja-collection\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150357SsA6iR92Y0VpFCO8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150357S9GBnJ27hkH0IuTl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"323\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.53833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150358pUQwACqv9DkGubxF.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150358XiwLBoQVNSsWnzFY.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"301\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}